"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Mother - I don't know how many people's hearts are held by the child's call. Yunshan is green and the river is vast. Maternal love is an eternal persistence. In my mind, there is always a trilogy about maternal love.\\n\\n \\n\\nPart I: Japanese\\n\\n \\n\\nOn the white Alps, a mother and daughter are dancing happily in this silver world. However, an avalanche put the mother and daughter in trouble. When they climbed out of the snow, fate played a fatal joke on them - they were dressed in silver gray and snowed all over the mountain, and missed the rescue plane several times. As time went on, hunger, cold and fear came one after another. At the critical moment of life and death, the mother resolutely cut her own artery and dyed the snow red with bright hot blood, paving a journey of life for her daughter.\\n\\n \\n\\nThis bloody maternal love is as bright as a fiery red sun, so brilliant and persistent.\\n\\n \\n\\nPart II: Monthly\\n\\n \\n\\nIn that beautiful and miserable autumn, a loud noise shook the valley. When people ran to the wrecked cable car, there was a miracle created by love - the mother held a child high in her hands, the child survived, but the mother died forever. Maybe miracles can't be the same, but mother performed another spectacular miracle. In the Tangshan earthquake, it was found that almost all mothers were doing the same posture.\\n\\n \\n\\n风在低语，浪在荡漾，月色洒下白夜。无论是近在咫尺，还是远在天边，所有的妈妈都希望今晚孩子梦中的旋律是柔和的。纵然跨越千山万水，也愿意抓住一片月光，走进孩子们的梦想。\\n\\n \\n\\n第三部分：星星\\n\\n \\n\\n一堆白瓜子，彻底惊醒了迷路的亡命之徒。是一位母亲为儿子的罪行一一击倒的瓜子仁。\\n\\n \\n\\n是的，母亲借着微弱的光，为流浪的孩子们系上了鞋子。她也希望有一天星星能让流浪的孩子们找到回家的路。\\n\\n \\n\\n这个世界上可能没有永恒的东西，但每个母亲总是用一根线绑着自己的孩子走在她心目中的街道上。不管岁月匆匆匆匆，都是孩子们心中的日月星辰，日月星辰构成了孩子们心中的天堂。\\n\\n \\n\\n天堂，爱情三部曲！\",\"timestamp\":1639147813,\"title\":\"MOTHER\"},\"digest\":\"teYJ6W4veLvUGoF9XmDP79hjQ83RpEl06HZ2ZSqyRoY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x3D99848423De7752368Daf4b5e7726d01728DF8f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Le-dk2rEXPHsHNRipbKZ_2462nODyyhY2LOi77A14ec\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"4u_kj5X3czPYg6PjSKrWKWAPY5XRNTRHFdpGkmjODrU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FaCHbqUNYkRwOk2krv2x69DLW42q3W6eYkntDXoU-oK2T3gLShrH5JuMRTAY4kLzBjnmiB2tEqntUefJ_LmPIQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc802023fbe7dcaad0ba030ec194eea26ab951561574c0a13af3367e90e07e5347d71cc975139a5b0877a16ff4220c705c6c4b4b9e550cebe8eb971c2d5aab9a91b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Le-dk2rEXPHsHNRipbKZ_2462nODyyhY2LOi77A14ec\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"4u_kj5X3czPYg6PjSKrWKWAPY5XRNTRHFdpGkmjODrU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"teYJ6W4veLvUGoF9XmDP79hjQ83RpEl06HZ2ZSqyRoY\"}"